-Drink this.
-I'm fine.


50
00:05:41,070 --> 00:05:44,110
What were you doing here anyway?


51
00:05:45,870 --> 00:05:48,740
Well, the thing is...


52
00:05:48,909 --> 00:05:51,810
It was raining, and I couldn't sleep.


53
00:05:51,909 --> 00:05:53,720
So I was taking a walk,


54
00:05:53,880 --> 00:05:57,050
and I happened to hear the window break
and someone scream.


55
00:05:58,390 --> 00:06:01,690
A strange coincidence, right?


56
00:06:03,360 --> 00:06:05,130
But you're lucky


57
00:06:05,190 --> 00:06:07,560
that I happened to pass by there
at that exact moment.


58
00:06:08,860 --> 00:06:11,170
Anyway, thank you so much.


59
00:06:11,630 --> 00:06:13,770
You should go home. It's late.


60
00:06:13,840 --> 00:06:15,640
Will you be okay?


61
