I can never relax here.


62
00:06:18,670 --> 00:06:20,580
You never know when something will happen.


63
00:06:22,680 --> 00:06:26,210
What I mean is...


64
00:06:26,410 --> 00:06:27,950
I'm okay now.


65
00:06:29,080 --> 00:06:32,090
All right. I'll get going then.


66
