202
00:16:15,270 --> 00:16:18,310
Ms. Sim Ae-soon, you can't go home
if you don't answer.


203
00:16:21,110 --> 00:16:22,280
Goodness.


204
00:16:28,580 --> 00:16:29,920
Yes, hello.


205
00:16:29,980 --> 00:16:33,290
This is Detective Lee Min-jae
from Jeju Police Station.


206
00:16:33,550 --> 00:16:36,820
You know, the townhouse employee
named Sim Ae-soon.


207
00:16:37,660 --> 00:16:40,290
Yes, her.
What is her resident registration number?


208
00:16:41,830 --> 00:16:43,930
She won't tell me.


209
00:16:44,430 --> 00:16:47,470
Yes, thank you. Bye.


210
00:16:54,310 --> 00:16:55,380
What?


211
00:16:56,180 --> 00:16:57,340
What is this?


212
00:17:02,350 --> 00:17:04,050
Push forward. Yes, forward.


213
00:17:04,349 --> 00:17:06,990
Yes. A bit lower.


214
00:17:07,220 --> 00:17:09,520
No, a little bit lower than that.


215
00:17:09,589 --> 00:17:10,890
Just a little bit more.


216
00:17:10,960 --> 00:17:12,730
The camera lens is on the front


217
00:17:12,790 --> 00:17:14,960
and if you open the back,


218
00:17:15,030 --> 00:17:17,460
-the memory card is in here.
-I see.


219
00:17:17,530 --> 00:17:19,329
If you insert this
in a memory card reader,


220
00:17:19,400 --> 00:17:21,339
you'll be able to play
the recorded videos.


221
00:17:21,700 --> 00:17:23,540
-Here.
-Thank you.


222
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:25,440
Call us if there's any problem
with the product.


223
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:27,640
-Okay. Thank you.
-We'll get going then.


224
00:17:55,240 --> 00:17:56,640
Yi-chan, look at this.


225
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:01,340
From now on,
if you have anything you want to say,


226
00:18:02,780 --> 00:18:05,010
write it here and show it to me.


227
00:18:05,510 --> 00:18:07,210
What do you think? Fun, right?


228
00:18:24,430 --> 00:18:27,970
[You were scared too, right, Mom?
I'm fine, so don't...]


229
00:18:32,910 --> 00:18:33,970
Are you done writing it?


230
00:18:35,640 --> 00:18:37,540
[You were scared too, right, Mom?]


231
00:18:37,950 --> 00:18:40,510
[I'm fine, so don't worry too much.]


232
00:18:47,420 --> 00:18:50,690
[I love you.]


233
00:18:52,730 --> 00:18:53,830
[I love you.]


234
00:19:02,170 --> 00:19:05,670
I'm fine as long as you are.


235
00:19:05,740 --> 00:19:09,240
You know I love you too, right?


236
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:16,680
You're so sweet.


237
00:20:24,120 --> 00:20:27,120
Yes, I've looked around but found nothing.


238
00:20:27,190 --> 00:20:28,820
I think it was a false alarm.


239
00:20:29,420 --> 00:20:30,960
Yes, thank you.


240
00:20:41,800 --> 00:20:44,710
-Oh, my gosh. Really? It was the helper?
-That's what she said.


241
00:20:44,770 --> 00:20:47,440
-The helper did it.
-Why do things like this keep happening?


242
00:20:47,510 --> 00:20:50,210
Mom, Yi-chan was absent yesterday
because he was sick.


243
00:20:50,280 --> 00:20:51,950
What? Sick where?


244
00:20:53,380 --> 00:20:56,650
I want to visit Yi-chan
if he's absent again today.


245
00:20:57,150 --> 00:20:58,350
I'm not too sure about that.


246
00:20:59,090 --> 00:21:01,420
I'll ask Yi-chan how he is.


247
00:21:01,620 --> 00:21:03,860
Yi-chan's mom might not let us see him.


248
00:21:03,920 --> 00:21:05,890
Isn't it because you don't want to go?


249
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:09,130
You haven't been hanging out with
Yi-chan's mom ever since you two fought.


250
00:21:10,830 --> 00:21:13,300
Can't you make up with her
and stay close again?


251
00:21:13,830 --> 00:21:17,370
Adults have things
that can't be solved with an apology.


252
00:21:17,440 --> 00:21:19,210
Why? What is that?


253
00:21:20,040 --> 00:21:22,810
You'll know once you grow up more.


254
00:21:23,810 --> 00:21:25,680
By the way Mom, what's adultery?


255
00:21:25,750 --> 00:21:28,380
What? Who said that word?


256
00:21:31,520 --> 00:21:32,720
The other kids.


257
00:21:39,490 --> 00:21:40,860
You don't need to know what that is.


258
00:21:41,030 --> 00:21:43,130
-Why?
-Because you don't.


