that my bad fate killed my husband.


515
00:38:08,310 --> 00:38:10,450
Did you hate me so much?


516
00:38:10,780 --> 00:38:12,750
So much that you threw a rock
in the middle of the night?


517
00:38:20,090 --> 00:38:22,900
Do you remember the woman you saw with me


518
00:38:22,960 --> 00:38:24,200
at the restaurant the other day?


519
00:38:25,430 --> 00:38:28,940
She asked me to help you.


520
00:38:29,900 --> 00:38:32,610
What's your relationship with her?


521
00:38:38,950 --> 00:38:40,750
I don't know her.


522
00:38:44,250 --> 00:38:47,650
I already told you.
I don't know anyone here.


523
00:39:01,100 --> 00:39:04,100
I won't report my husband's death.


524
00:39:04,870 --> 00:39:07,070
As you said, I thought for a moment


525
00:39:07,640 --> 00:39:10,610
of letting him go and leaving Jeju.


526
00:39:11,440 --> 00:39:12,880
But I decided not to.


527
00:39:12,950 --> 00:39:14,480
What's the reason?


528
00:39:14,550 --> 00:39:15,850
A year ago,


529
00:39:16,180 --> 00:39:18,950
I didn't really know anything
about my husband's death.


530
00:39:19,490 --> 00:39:21,050
No, I pretended not to.


531
00:39:21,790 --> 00:39:24,290
But I can't repeat that again.


532
00:39:24,360 --> 00:39:27,830
If there's something
I must take responsibility for, I will.


533
00:39:28,530 --> 00:39:31,660
I'll no longer hide behind his death
and run away.


534
00:39:33,970 --> 00:39:36,200
What will you do
with the foundation's lawsuit?


535
00:39:36,500 --> 00:39:40,310
I'll talk to the new chairman
once someone has been appointed.


536
00:39:44,840 --> 00:39:48,150
It's a shame, but I understand.


537
00:39:48,450 --> 00:39:50,380
My work is finished here.


538
00:40:04,200 --> 00:40:07,230
Sit down. I asked you to come
because I have something to tell you.


539
00:40:16,440 --> 00:40:18,040
I got a will


540
00:40:18,540 --> 00:40:21,310
from a representative to report his death.


541
00:40:21,550 --> 00:40:22,780
A will?


542
00:40:23,280 --> 00:40:25,580
Why would a will suddenly appear now?


543
00:40:26,790 --> 00:40:28,620
And what about reporting his death?


544
00:40:29,160 --> 00:40:31,690
He asked the representative
to deliver it to me a year later.


545
00:40:31,760 --> 00:40:34,860
Since we can legally report his death now.


546
00:40:35,230 --> 00:40:36,930
He wishes to be freed.


547
00:40:37,000 --> 00:40:38,930
He really said that?


548
00:40:39,930 --> 00:40:42,800
What else did he say? Was that everything?


549
00:40:44,370 --> 00:40:48,370
There's nothing we can do
about running into each other like this,


550
00:40:49,480 --> 00:40:52,340
but I thought you should know too.


551
00:40:53,380 --> 00:40:56,620
And I'm not going to proceed
with that will.


552
00:40:56,680 --> 00:40:58,080
Who are you to decide that?


553
00:40:58,150 --> 00:41:00,850
Because I'm his legal spouse.


554
00:41:00,920 --> 00:41:01,990
That's it.


555
00:41:03,760 --> 00:41:05,260
Legal spouse?


556
00:41:06,560 --> 00:41:08,260
We got married too.


557
00:41:08,490 --> 00:41:11,130
He made his vows with me too.


558
00:41:11,560 --> 00:41:13,170
Should you really be saying that to me?


559
00:41:13,230 --> 00:41:14,530
I'm only stating the facts.


560
00:41:14,600 --> 00:41:16,840
Don't you have a conscience or any shame?


561
00:41:16,900 --> 00:41:19,110
Can't you see anything but yourself?


562
00:41:19,570 --> 00:41:21,210
He already had a family.


563
00:41:21,270 --> 00:41:24,410
What does that man mean to you
to throw away yourself like this?


564
00:41:24,480 --> 00:41:26,250
You're not his only family.


565
00:41:26,680 --> 00:41:28,450
Don't talk about us in that dismissive way


566
00:41:28,510 --> 00:41:30,420
when you knew nothing until now.


567
00:41:31,480 --> 00:41:32,890
-What?
-Nothing is more important


568
00:41:32,950 --> 00:41:34,520
than my feelings for him.


569
00:41:34,850 --> 00:41:37,360
That's what he meant to me.


570
00:41:37,420 --> 00:41:40,360
Stop it. I can't bear it anymore.


571
00:41:40,660 --> 00:41:43,160
Just listening to you gives me goosebumps.


572
00:42:51,830 --> 00:42:53,300
Will you be with me


573
00:42:54,630 --> 00:42:56,040
for the rest of my life?


574
00:43:43,550 --> 00:43:46,120
Ma'am, are you quitting your job?


575
00:43:46,190 --> 00:43:49,720
It's only natural they ask me to leave
after something like that happened.


576
00:43:55,560 --> 00:43:58,900
You should also leave this place
as soon as you can


577
00:43:58,960 --> 00:44:00,600
before anything worse happens.


578
00:44:03,500 --> 00:44:05,470
Is that why you did that?


579
00:44:05,800 --> 00:44:07,410
To make me leave this place?


580
00:44:10,880 --> 00:44:13,650
Why? Why should I leave this place?


581
00:44:17,820 --> 00:44:18,950
Ma'am.


582
00:44:19,690 --> 00:44:22,090
Please tell me something.


583
00:44:22,720 --> 00:44:25,660
I didn't break the window.


584
00:44:27,430 --> 00:44:28,630
What do you--


585
00:44:28,890 --> 00:44:31,030
If it wasn't you, who was it?


586
00:44:31,100 --> 00:44:33,030
Someone else was there...


587
00:44:35,930 --> 00:44:37,900
watching your house.


588
00:44:40,340 --> 00:44:41,440
Who was it?


589
00:44:42,340 --> 00:44:45,110
Why didn't you tell me?


590
00:44:45,180 --> 00:44:47,050
Even if I did...


591
00:46:40,060 --> 00:46:43,400
So this is your scariest memory.


592
00:46:43,460 --> 00:46:44,730
Can I have a look, Yi-chan?


593
00:46:49,270 --> 00:46:52,100
Was this night scary
because of the thunder and lightning?


594
00:46:53,410 --> 00:46:54,570
Then what scared you?


595
00:47:05,680 --> 00:47:09,520
[Art Therapy Room]


596
00:47:08,220 --> 00:47:09,250
Let's go.


597
00:47:09,590 --> 00:47:13,490
[Art Therapy Room]


598
00:47:11,720 --> 00:47:13,730
He did well in today's class too.


599
00:47:13,790 --> 00:47:15,390
Great. Thank you.


600
00:47:15,460 --> 00:47:16,660
See you next time.


601
00:47:15,690 --> 00:47:18,000
[Art Therapy Room]


602
00:47:16,730 --> 00:47:18,630
Make sure
you finish your drawing from today.


603
00:47:19,730 --> 00:47:20,900
-Take care.
-You too.


604
00:47:19,770 --> 00:47:21,200
[Art Therapy Room]


605
00:47:21,770 --> 00:47:23,470
Let's go.


606
00:47:37,450 --> 00:47:38,780
His phone.


607
00:47:48,090 --> 00:47:49,260
Yi-chan.


608
00:47:51,400 --> 00:47:52,500
Yi-chan.


609
00:47:53,000 --> 00:47:55,400
Did you take Daddy's cell phone
by any chance?


610
00:47:57,000 --> 00:47:58,400
You really didn't take it?


611
00:48:12,750 --> 00:48:14,620
[This time, it really wasn't me.]


612
00:48:19,690 --> 00:48:21,330
Then where did it go?


613
00:49:16,680 --> 00:49:18,350
I had flipped this face-down.


614
00:49:29,190 --> 00:49:30,000
[File]


615
00:49:32,100 --> 00:49:32,900
[File]


616
00:50:13,740 --> 00:50:16,640
-Send over the data from this camera.
-Sure.


617
00:50:17,780 --> 00:50:19,080
I'll check that one over there.


618
00:50:52,580 --> 00:50:56,280
We've checked everything.
Nothing else was caught on camera.


619
00:50:56,750 --> 00:50:59,280
Is anything else missing
other than the cell phone?


620
00:50:59,350 --> 00:51:00,550
No, nothing.


621
00:51:00,720 --> 00:51:02,120
Everything else is still here.


622
00:51:02,350 --> 00:51:03,420
All of our valuables too.


623
00:51:03,490 --> 00:51:06,560
But there was no sign of anyone
entering from the outside.


624
00:51:07,460 --> 00:51:08,760
That's impossible.


625
00:51:09,390 --> 00:51:10,860
No one came in?


626
00:51:10,930 --> 00:51:15,130
That's right. If someone had picked
the lock and forced their way in,


627
00:51:15,700 --> 00:51:18,240
the center would have received an alert.


628
00:51:20,870 --> 00:51:23,010
Why don't you call the police
if you're worried?


629
00:51:23,140 --> 00:51:25,840
-No, it's okay. I'll take care of it.
-Sure.


630
00:51:26,310 --> 00:51:27,950
Then if there's nothing else,


631
00:51:28,010 --> 00:51:29,380
-we'll get going now.
-Okay.


632
00:51:29,450 --> 00:51:30,950
-Thank you.
-No problem.


633
00:51:32,150 --> 00:51:33,220
Let's go.


634
00:51:42,630 --> 00:51:44,300
-Hello?
[-It's me.]


635
00:51:44,860 --> 00:51:46,670
I'm here now,


636
00:51:44,860 --> 00:51:49,170
[Caution, Beware of Cliff Falls]


637
00:51:46,970 --> 00:51:49,300
but maybe it was too long ago.


638
00:51:49,370 --> 00:51:51,740
No one really remembers Sim Ae-soon.


639
00:51:52,340 --> 00:51:54,010
[So don't get your hopes up.]


640
00:51:54,110 --> 00:51:55,970
[I'll do a little more digging
before I head back.]


641
00:51:56,170 --> 00:51:57,280
Everything's okay, right?


642
00:52:00,310 --> 00:52:01,650
What do you mean?


643
00:52:02,150 --> 00:52:03,350
What was caught on camera?


644
00:52:05,580 --> 00:52:07,020
I'm sure it was nothing.


645
00:52:07,390 --> 00:52:10,190
The security company came
and checked everything.


646
00:52:10,260 --> 00:52:11,360
They said everything was fine.


647
00:52:12,490 --> 00:52:14,930
I've been so scatterbrained
for the past few days.


648
00:52:15,230 --> 00:52:16,800
I even lost his phone.


649
00:52:18,000 --> 00:52:20,370
[Caution, Beware of Cliff Falls]


650
00:52:24,940 --> 00:52:28,110
Well, I have something to confess.


651
00:52:28,840 --> 00:52:29,880
First,


652
00:52:30,210 --> 00:52:32,610
[promise me that you won't get angry.]


653
00:52:32,780 --> 00:52:34,850
You know, when I returned


654
00:52:35,510 --> 00:52:38,180
the cell phone to you on Camp Day,


655
00:52:38,250 --> 00:52:41,920
I had installed a tracking app
and a spy app on the phone.


656
00:52:42,890 --> 00:52:45,360
I was hired to monitor you,


657
00:52:46,320 --> 00:52:47,760
so I had no choice.


658
00:52:49,800 --> 00:52:50,960
I'm sorry.


659
00:52:52,630 --> 00:52:54,270
Is that why


660
00:52:55,070 --> 00:52:58,340
you always showed up like Superman
when anything happened?


661
00:52:59,300 --> 00:53:01,840
This is a clear violation
of the Location Information Protection Act


662
00:53:01,910 --> 00:53:05,580
and the Communications Privacy Act.
You know that this is a crime, right?


663
00:53:05,880 --> 00:53:07,610
Wiretapping and surveillance
are serious felonies.


664
00:53:07,680 --> 00:53:09,280
Yes, I know. Of course, I'm aware.


665
00:53:09,550 --> 00:53:11,380
Anyway, that's not the problem now.


666
00:53:11,450 --> 00:53:13,190
Hold on. Let me check.


667
00:53:14,950 --> 00:53:16,590
[Ashbun Town House 7041,
Gueok-ri, Daejeong-eup, Seogwipo, Jeju]


668
00:53:16,660 --> 00:53:18,390
[Search Completed]


669
00:53:17,160 --> 00:53:18,420
It's in...


670
00:53:19,060 --> 00:53:21,160
[the townhouse.]


671
00:53:21,230 --> 00:53:22,730
The phone is in your house.


672
00:53:23,060 --> 00:53:24,130
It is?


673
00:53:25,060 --> 00:53:26,900
Did I put it somewhere and forget?


674
00:53:27,500 --> 00:53:28,970
Let me try calling it again.


675
00:54:08,970 --> 00:54:10,410
[Please leave a message after...]


676
00:54:18,720 --> 00:54:20,320
-Hi.
-Did you find it?


677
00:54:20,390 --> 00:54:22,790
I heard it, but it's a wall.


678
00:54:22,850 --> 00:54:24,390
A wall? What do you mean?


679
00:54:24,490 --> 00:54:27,160
I heard it ring from inside the wall,
then it stopped.


680
00:54:40,570 --> 00:54:43,010
Hello? Mr. Oh, are you still there?


681
00:54:43,070 --> 00:54:45,240
Ms. Song, I'll come right now.


682
00:54:45,310 --> 00:54:46,650
Take your son and get out of there.


683
00:54:46,750 --> 00:54:48,380
Why? What's going on?


684
00:54:48,450 --> 00:54:50,120
Just get out of the house, now!


685
00:54:50,180 --> 00:54:52,280
[Caution, Beware of Cliff Falls]


686
00:54:50,550 --> 00:54:51,520
Darn it.


687
00:55:33,790 --> 00:55:35,760
Mom!


688
00:56:11,260 --> 00:56:12,330
It's coming from around here.


689
00:57:06,020 --> 00:57:07,190
Oh my gosh...


690
00:57:10,090 --> 00:57:12,120
What... What is this?


691
00:58:08,250 --> 00:58:09,810
[23 minutes]


692
00:58:28,370 --> 00:58:30,770
Someone was just here.


693
00:59:13,510 --> 00:59:16,010
[72km, 1 hour]


694
00:59:38,600 --> 00:59:40,040
The person already fled.


695
00:59:40,710 --> 00:59:42,740
And there are no cameras around the exit.


696
01:00:00,890 --> 01:00:03,930
Who on earth did this?


697
01:00:31,720 --> 01:00:34,490
[High Class]


698
01:00:34,590 --> 01:00:36,490
[This place was left for me
by my husband.]


699
01:00:36,690 --> 01:00:39,800
[His legal wife? You can keep that title.]


700
01:00:40,000 --> 01:00:41,070
[The board will file a suit]


701
01:00:41,130 --> 01:00:43,400
[for the foundation's investment losses.]


702
01:00:43,570 --> 01:00:44,700
[Enjoy.]


703
01:00:44,770 --> 01:00:46,700
It's what your husband left for you.


704
01:00:49,010 --> 01:00:51,810
[Tell Mommy what you saw that day.
Who is this person?]


705
01:00:52,710 --> 01:00:54,950
[Whoever that is,
I'll help you look for them.]


706
01:00:55,010 --> 01:00:56,910
[I want you to come
to the station with me.]


707
01:00:56,980 --> 01:00:59,620
[-Apparently, Danny Oh isn't Danny Oh.]
-Darn it!


708
01:01:00,050 --> 01:01:02,050
[I'm determined to find out]


709
01:01:02,120 --> 01:01:05,660
[what's happening to that house
and who was there.]


